### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → CREDIT LEDGER — /api/v1/admin/ledger
### ============================================================================

### Get credit ledger
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/ledger?userId=&companyId=
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Adjust credits
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/ledger/adjust
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "amount": 100,
  "reason": "Manual adjustment"
}
